videos.headline: Sam Darnold stuffed on fourth down
videos.description: On fourth-and-one, USC QB Sam Darnold is tackled just inches shy of the first down, causing a turnover on downs.

videos.headline: Trojans scoop and score muffed punt for TD
videos.description: Arizona punter Josh Pollack can't handle the snap and has his punt attempt blocked by Michael Pittman Jr., and John Houston Jr. picks the ball up and returns it 11 yards for a USC touchdown.

videos.headline: Sam Darnold picked off in end zone
videos.description: With USC at Arizona's 1-yard line, Sam Darnold throws to the end zone and has his pass intercepted by Dane Cruikshank.

videos.headline: Darnold throws a strike to Vaughns for Trojans TD
videos.description: Sam Darnold connects with Tyler Vaughns over the middle and Vaughns takes it in for a 22-yard score, putting USC up 14-3.

videos.headline: USC's Mitchell lays out to haul in TD
videos.description: Sam Darnold throws to the end zone and connects with Steven Mitchell Jr. who dives to make the 27-yard touchdown grab.

videos.headline: Helton: Trojans need 'better efficiency in red zone'
videos.description: USC head coach Clay Helton was happy with his team's first-half performance, but says the team needs to do a better job converting in the red zone.

videos.headline: Wildcats' Ellison lays out to haul in tipped ball
videos.description: Khalil Tate has his pass tipped in the air and Tony Ellison dives to grab the ball just before it hits the ground for an 11-yard pickup.

videos.headline: USC VS ARIZ
Darnold connects with Burnett to set up Trojans in red zone
videos.description: Sam Darnold finds a wide-open Deontay Burnett along the right sideline, and Burnett takes it all the way down to the 5-yard line for a big 41-yard pickup.

videos.headline: Jones pounds it in for USC TD
videos.description: Ronald Jones II takes a handoff and bowls through an Arizona defender en route to a 5-yard touchdown, giving the Trojans a commanding 28-6 lead.

videos.headline: Tate breaks free for Wildcats TD
videos.description: Arizona QB Khalil Tate uses his legs and scrambles past multiple USC defenders to score from 32 yards out.

videos.headline: Arizona's Tate evades pressure, finds WR for TD
videos.description: Khalil Tate escapes from the pocket and throws off balance to connect with Shun Brown for a 30-yard score, cutting the Wildcats' deficit to eight.

videos.headline: Ware tiptoes along sideline for Trojans TD
videos.description: Aca'Cedric Ware takes a handoff and outruns the defense along the left sideline for a 42-yard touchdown, giving USC a 35-20 lead.

videos.headline: USC VS ARIZ
Taylor jukes defender en route to Wildcats TD
videos.description: Khalil Tate completes a short pass to J.J. Taylor who makes a defender whiff and takes it to the house for a 16-yard score.

videos.headline: Wildcats tie it up with Green TD and 2-point conversion
videos.description: Zach Green rushes in for a 3-yard touchdown, then Arizona goes for two and Khalil Tate connects with Tony Ellison to convert, tying the game at 35.

videos.headline: Jones' 2nd TD of game gives Trojans 4th quarter lead
videos.description: Ronald Jones II pounds it in from a yard out to put USC ahead 42-35.

videos.headline: Trojans pick off Tate in the fourth quarter
videos.description: Khalil Tate goes deep, but has his pass intercepted by Ajene Harris.

videos.headline: Jones breaks loose to set up USC at goal line
videos.description: Ronald Jones II rips off a huge run, getting all the way down to the Arizona 1-yard line on a 52-yard pickup.

videos.headline: Jones extends Trojans' lead with 3rd TD of game
videos.description: Ronald Jones II pounds it in from a yard out to put USC ahead 49-35.

videos.headline: USC's Houston rips ball from WR for INT
videos.description: Khalil Tate has his pass picked off after John Houston Jr. steals the ball out of an Arizona receiver's hands.

videos.headline: Darnold: Offense 'got into rhythm' in fourth quarter
videos.description: USC quarterback Sam Darnold praised his team's resilient win over Arizona, saying the offense got hot in the fourth quarter in the 49-35 victory.

videos.headline: Trojans outlast Wildcats
videos.description: Rod Gilmore and Mark Jones break down USC's 49-35 win over Arizona, citing the Trojans' fourth quarter offensive outburst as the key to victory.
